<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.4">
<l>tuḷakka milcuṭa raiyavu ṇaṉuṭal</l>
<l>piḷakkum maintaṉaip pērilva ṇaṅki<supplied>p</supplied>pō</l>
<l>yaḷappi lāramu taiyama rarkkaruḷ</l>
<l>viḷakki ṉaiceṉṟu veḷḷaṟaik kāṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone worshipping in Pēr the inextinguishable light,</l>
<l>The man[-lion] who split open the demon’s body,</l>
<l>We will go and see the limitless abundant nectar,</l>
<l>The lamp of grace for immortals in Veḷḷaṟai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
